er.-Credit-Frank-Hoensch-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Frank-Turner.-Credit-Frank-Hoensch-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Frank-Turner.-Credit-Frank-Hoensch-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Frank-Turner.-Credit-Frank-Hoensch-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Frank-Turner.-Credit-Frank-Hoensch-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-turner">弗兰克·特纳 (Frank Turner)</a>与音乐场馆信托基金 (Music Venue Trust) 合作，将在他即将到来的英国巡演中每售出一张门票，就会向基层场馆捐赠 1 英镑。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-grassroots-music-venues-touring-collapse-mvt-steve-lamacq-budget-help-3808675"><strong>英国草根场馆遭受“巡演彻底崩溃”之苦——以下是您可以提供帮助的方法</strong></a></li></ul><p>上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-turner">Frank Turner</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-sleeping-souls">The Sleeping Souls</a>宣布将于 2025 年进行英国巡演。</p><p>今天（12月17日），特纳在社交媒体上写道：“对于即将到来的四月巡演，我很自豪地说我已经与@musicvenuetrust的老朋友合作了。每张门票中的 1 英镑将用于支持当地的独立音乐场所。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDrJXnoMA5M/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"